Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.68,0:00:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在風的節奏中推理漸漸清晰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的糾結也可以解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.67,0:00:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗組織和寶石強匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件在抽絲剝繭中接近真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.65,0:00:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.55,0:00:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從被殺害的板倉先生的日記中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.92,0:01:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解到有關黑暗組織的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.69,0:01:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我和博士來到了板倉的別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在那裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏特加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.69,0:02:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.95,0:02:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這別墅裡接收郵件的事被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.41,0:02:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！快說話啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.77,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你就在別墅裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.02,0:02:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.66,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回答我 板倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.01,0:02:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與黑暗組織的接觸（追跡篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！快說話啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.59,0:02:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你就在別墅裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回答我 板倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.34,0:02:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖…雖然有點危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.15,0:03:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也只能冒著暴風雪從後門溜出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.19,0:03:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是抱歉 在黑暗中一時找不到電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.88,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好像因為暴風雪來襲而停電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛剛的郵件沒有接收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你跑到深山的別墅去接收郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.35,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果停電為什麼答錄機還能啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.08,0:03:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為一下雪這裡經常會停電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我使用了內部裝電池的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.27,0:03:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你知道的還真清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.94,0:03:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一舉一動都在我們的掌握之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,350)\fad(300,300)}（把燈打開）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不會一直在監視這棟別墅吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和約好的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會騷擾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你完成了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？有人在你旁邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.45,0:04:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.28,0:04:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是風的聲音 剛剛風打到窗戶的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為你那邊的雪下得很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.64,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在無法使用電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你就直接告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交軟體的時間和地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.56,0:04:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！沒辦法 我可只說一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仔細聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道有個還在施工中的賢橋車站吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以後道路和地鐵的連結點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天淩晨12點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個車站最下層的0032寄物櫃前碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了帶那個軟體來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天下午辦了住院手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.53,0:05:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我的心臟不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會還沒完成那個軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想藉機拖延時間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能？我已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你哪天方便？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.73,0:05:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概要住3到4天 可能要5天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！我可等不了那麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.99,0:05:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去延遲你的住院時間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易才預約到了一位著名的心臟外科醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法改時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要我在住院前交給你的話就只有今晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天的話工人會到車站工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣反而對你們不利吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就4點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個小時之後也就是淩晨4點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把軟體帶到我剛剛講的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四、四個小時？要我從群馬趕到東京？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然已經完成了 應該可以拿來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在四個小時後抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們不准在那裡提前埋伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我看到了你們的同夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次交易立刻終止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們要硬搶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.96,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會知道這個軟體怎麼用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.45,0:06:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！和瞭解的一樣 你這個人還真是謹慎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼四個小時以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.46,0:06:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在賢橋車站地下的0032寄物櫃前碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別遲到哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.25,0:06:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上鉤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你到底想幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你真的要聽他們的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把軟體拿去給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會聽他們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是引誘他把交貨時間提前到淩晨4點而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假裝著急的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.44,0:07:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞不就開始報導板倉先生被殺的消息了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事要是被那些傢伙們知道的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.57,0:07:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個交易和那些傢伙的線索可能又會斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.60,0:07:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好目前還沒有媒體報導板倉的新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你一開始就這麼打算嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.56,0:07:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就打算收到他們的郵件之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回信要求提早交易的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.44,0:07:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把我們到過這裡的所有痕跡擦掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後博士你去開車我們趕緊離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.85,0:07:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.86,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那些傢伙不是在附近監視這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我們光明正大地開著車離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙說不定會看見我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伏特加和他的同夥在監視這棟房子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.93,0:08:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為停電而無法使用電腦的這句謊話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定馬上就會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.74,0:08:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才叫我把燈打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.41,0:08:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來至少可以肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.15,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近沒有他們的同夥在監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們之所以會知道這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是安裝了收件者沒有打開郵件的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.12,0:08:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會自動追蹤收件人所在地的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少已經掌握到那些傢伙的線索了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要用博士車上的筆記型電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查這個軟體裡的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是能用來記錄犯下的重大案件的資料的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就馬上通知警方埋伏在交易地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.55,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到他們來拿軟體時就能一網打盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.46,0:09:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個軟體也被設定了密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.82,0:09:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟那封郵件一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能板倉和那些傢伙事先設定了密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就先複製起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為複製檔案也需要密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就沒有證據給警方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙不是經常帶著槍嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用非法攜帶槍械的名義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣警方至少會出動兩三名警察吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們不知道對方會來多少人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.32,0:09:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算找出他們的犯罪證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓警方知道是一個多麼龐大的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.43,0:09:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去破壞他們的計畫並逮捕他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在已經不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是急死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知道那些傢伙會在那裡出現卻無計可施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.46,0:09:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你該不會想直接跟他們見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.08,0:10:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 博士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是爆胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.12,0:10:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好打電話給離這裡最近的加油站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請他們馬上送備胎過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候在這個地方不可能馬上過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們就坐在車裡慢慢等好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就趕不上交易時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.18,0:10:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是神叫新一你不要去做那麼危險的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車…車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.23,0:10:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.39,0:10:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我的車子爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想回到東京去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以載我們一程嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.11,0:11:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 反正順路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 這附近的路你熟悉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大叔就坐在副駕駛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟就坐後面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 大姐姐 吵到妳睡覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我只是躺一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.96,0:11:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是外國車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大哥哥你的車嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已經開得有點膩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近正想換一部新車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.87,0:12:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你一定很有錢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這車很貴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.27,0:12:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起來不怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.97,0:12:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一個大公司的繼承人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.00,0:12:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.89,0:12:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積雪的道路真是可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急 安全駕駛最重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你們剛剛有沒有聽到奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.22,0:12:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎？我什麼也沒聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是堆在後車箱的行李吧 不要介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！不要吸煙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭煙味！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 我一時忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往東京的方向要向左轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.31,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪已經停了 我想3點前應該可以到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們為什麼來群馬縣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶孫子來滑雪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不算是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你專心開好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.04,0:13:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不該走積雪的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.89,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這兩個人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小心一點好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.39,0:14:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始已經有不少車子向我們按喇叭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長在雪路上開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車還沒進行車檢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要更小心開車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛車差不多該車檢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.02,0:14:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車窗前的擋風玻璃上不是寫著"2"的標誌嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個標誌叫做車檢標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.83,0:14:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用數字和顏色提示人們什麼時候該去車檢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的標誌顏色是今年的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.41,0:14:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你應該要在今年2月份之前去做車檢才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.56,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月我剛收到去做車檢的通知單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小弟弟 那個標誌你什麼時候看見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它應該都被雪蓋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.48,0:15:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.43,0:15:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要對面有車開來就可以看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過車燈的光線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能看到表面的數字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是從背面看到的"2"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.02,0:15:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實應該是"5"才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.52,0:15:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好奇怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.05,0:15:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你怎麼會收到2月之前做車檢的通知呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…那是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你們說過了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個有錢的少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那些事都是交給別人去做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才是隨便說說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.91,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他自己根本從沒注意過車檢的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有在這裡右轉的話要到東京可就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都是小弟弟你太囉嗦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.90,0:16:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這個孩子的好奇心就是太旺盛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始你一直在聽什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收音機的新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 報導了很多的新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是景氣復甦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BIG大阪隊的新教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有逃亡中的寶石搶匪等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.09,0:16:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不簡單啊 這麼小的年齡就喜歡聽新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.84,0:16:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.85,0:16:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？那個寶石搶匪落網了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞報導說他們可能還在群馬縣附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一定可以馬上被逮捕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.59,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看現在到處都有路檢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請出示駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您是從哪裡過來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這不是山村警官嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是柯南嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山村警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.34,0:17:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是為了抓住寶石搶匪所設的路檢對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.30,0:17:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三個搶匪帶著面具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶劫了一家珠寶店之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.69,0:17:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們把作案用的贓車丟棄在山裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就消失的無影無蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.01,0:17:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那三個人裡其中一個人受了傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想應該不會逃得太遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.66,0:18:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到消息時我正好在附近巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.32,0:18:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從寶石店跑出的搶匪被我撞了個正著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我拿出槍衝著他們大喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.75,0:18:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 不然的話我就要開槍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.52,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們不聽警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就開了一槍打算嚇唬他們一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.01,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.65,0:18:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣 沒想到剛好打中其中一名犯人的大腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.90,0:18:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳…總之他們可能是開著事先準備好的其他車輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.11,0:18:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是搶了路上來往的車子逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.21,0:18:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你們有沒有看到這種可疑的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是坐在別人車上的人對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的車在山中壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請剛好路過的這位先生讓我們搭個便車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.56,0:19:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你的車呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.95,0:19:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打電話給修車場 他們說早上才會把車拖走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把鑰匙掛在車上扔到山裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.77,0:19:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你的車不是很危險嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.77,0:19:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被那些搶匪發現說不定會被開走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你不用管我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是快去看看那輛車比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一台黃色的金龜車很好找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.89,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像在哪裡聽到過你們的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.24,0:19:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以走了嗎 警官？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.64,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 蓋在你大腿上的外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿下來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在懷疑我們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看沒有中槍的痕跡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.46,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那麼路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這裡是阿笠家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群馬縣員警？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.18,0:20:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然阿笠先生已經叫修車廠早上來把車子拖走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我怕車子繼續放在山裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.07,0:20:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會被逃亡中的搶匪給開走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.41,0:20:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此先叫拖吊車把車子移開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.82,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請轉告他來群馬縣警局這邊取車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.95,0:20:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了 幹嘛要開車去群馬？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.14,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又是被工藤找去調查某件案件去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪費睡覺的時間管那麼多閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探真的有那麼好玩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備用的追蹤眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.86,0:21:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 交貨的時間提前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間是一小時後的凌晨4點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.49,0:21:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點不變還是在賢橋車站地下寄物櫃前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟琴酒大哥說一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多找點人手 帶槍來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.95,0:22:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙說不定會嚇得叫警方過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.85,0:22:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們原本就打算在交易後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.20,0:22:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在賢橋車站把他幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.28,0:23:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 時間快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.24,0:23:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都到齊了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.42,0:23:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.40,0:23:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一隻老鼠也不准放過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.45,0:24:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.92,0:24:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還在這附近窺視著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.65,0:24:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.00,0:24:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與黑暗組織的接觸（決死篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.99,0:24:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.34,0:24:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄物櫃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.47,0:24:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回終於要和他們見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.34,0:24:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形可不太好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.21,0:24:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.72,0:00:30.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海風中感覺到你的氣息 銀色的波浪消除了二人的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.73,0:00:43.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣讓時間停止吧 遠遠看去藐小的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.29,0:00:53.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法再分離 與你約定在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.63,0:01:00.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀的季節中得來不易的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.09,0:01:08.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再迷惘 相信我的眼神 風的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.31,0:01:15.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在溢滿的不安中隱藏淚水的昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.98,0:01:25.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠的回憶現在終於可以說出 風的啦啦啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.34,0:22:35.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到你的電話聲 如此堅強的我也會哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.35,0:22:42.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管彼此傷害對方 但是還是想見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.75,0:22:48.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使結局終究令人厭惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.61,0:22:55.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對於給我的回答覺得為難吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.54,0:23:04.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次回想起你那無法掩藏的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.58,0:23:08.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…I miss you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.21,0:23:21.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想明天 希望能夠相信 即使路途坎坷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.23,0:23:30.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想明天 你的全部 希望能夠見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.77,0:23:39.18,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到了只剩樹蔭間陽光搖曳的日子
